{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::44493161844::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Balearic Islands, Spain\n\nDISCOVER MALLORCA FROM A NEW PERSPECTIVE\n\nLUXURY DAY CHARTER ABOARD THE ABACUS 70 – FROM PORTALS NOUS\n\nEmbark on an extraordinary journey aboard the Abacus 70, a stunning 22-meter yacht that perfectly blends Italian design, power, and elegance. Based in Portals Nous, one of the most prestigious marinas in Mallorca, this is your invitation to explore the island’s southern and southwestern coast in complete luxury.\n\nFrom the moment you step aboard, you'll be surrounded by spacious lounges, sunbathing areas, and refined interiors—designed for comfort, style, and unforgettable moments at sea. During your full-day (8h) charter, our experienced captain will tailor the route to your preferences, revealing hidden coves, turquoise waters, and the island’s most breathtaking anchorages.\n\nDive into crystal-clear waters, relax on the flybridge with panoramic views, or enjoy time on deck with the sea as your backdrop. The yacht comes fully equipped with 2 stand up paddle boards, snorkeling gear, and everything you need for an incredible day on the water.\n\nIdeal for family outings, stylish celebrations, or romantic escapes, the Abacus 70 promises a charter experience like no other—refined, relaxing, and truly Mallorcan.\n\n• Departures from Portals Nous – just minutes from Palma\n\nLUXURY & COMFORT ABOARD THE ABACUS 70\n\nSpacious Motor Yacht for Charter – Accommodates up to 8 Guests\nThe Abacus 70 offers elegant living spaces designed for both day charters and multi-day getaways. With accommodation for up to 8 adults across 4 well-appointed cabins—2 doubles and 2 twins, each with an ensuite bathroom—this yacht is perfect for families or groups of friends looking to explore Mallorca in style. Step into a split-level saloon featuring two long, plush sofas, dining tables, and a Smart TV connected to an integrated sound system with Bluetooth Soundbox. International TV channels and internet access are also available onboard for your entertainment. The fully equipped galley includes a fridge, freezer, oven, hob, microwave, grill, and washing machine—everything you need for longer stays on the water.\n\nOutside, the flybridge offers a sunbed and seating area ideal for sunbathing and enjoying panoramic sea views. At the aft deck, a large dining table sets the scene for al fresco meals, while the spacious swim platform is your gateway to fun with water toys like water skis, kneeboard, donut, paddleboard, and snorkeling gear. Make the most of your Mediterranean escape aboard the Abacus 70—where comfort, elegance, and fun meet.","blueprint":{"name":"AURY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6::assets::2ffffbb0-c46d-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6::assets::2ffd8ab0-c46d-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6::assets::2ffe4e01-c46d-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6::assets::300049d1-c46d-11f0-9344-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6::assets::2ffcee70-c46d-11f0-9343-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6::assets::2ffc0410-c46d-11f0-9343-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6::assets::2ffb8ee0-c46d-11f0-9342-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6::assets::2ffc2b20-c46d-11f0-9342-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c469-11f0-b109-290dbc5867e6::assets::2ffd1580-c46d-11f0-9343-2b07eb4d16a9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::13e06a90-c46